queries.sql: SELECT sum(total_harga) as hasil_ttl, DATE_FORMAT(tgl_transaksi, "%Y-%M-%d") as tgl_transaksiz, `id_jenis_kayu`, `tgl_transaksi` FROM `db_transaksi` WHERE `tgl_transaksi` LIKE '%2022-09%' ESCAPE '!' GROUP BY `tgl_transaksiz` ORDER BY `tgl_transaksi` DESC
